title: Historic Jamestowne Part of Colonial National Historical Park: Planning
body: Planning       Historic Jamestowne, a part of Colonial National Historical Park (CNHP), provides the following park documents in fulfillment of the Electronic Freedom of Information Act Amendments of 1996 (EFOIA, 5 USC 552(2)).          CNHP Compendium List superintendents-authorized decisions that affect the public         Jamestown Long Range Interpretive Plan (LRIP) 2009 The Long Range Interpretive Plan (2009) provides direction for Jamestown's interpretive program for the next 5+ years.
